  "instructions": [
    "Melt the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the ginger and garlic and saut\u00143e until fragrant.",
    "Add the coriander and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the binchotan charcoal and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the shallots and stir for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the fish sauce and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add the eggs and stir until cooked through.",
    "Add the all-purpose flour and cornstarch and stir until a dough forms.",
    "Knead the dough for 5 minutes until smooth.",
    "Wrap the dough in plastic wrap and let rest for 10 minutes.",
    "Divide the dough into 8 equal pieces.",
    "Roll each piece into a ball and then flatten into a disk.",
    "Heat a large skillet over medium heat and cook the dough disks for 2-3 minutes on each side until golden brown.",
    "Serve warm."
